Investment Structure
Below is an example of our Target Mezzanine Structure:
Security: Secured/Unsecured
Cash interest rate: 12% - 14%
PIK interest rate: 2% - 3%
Closing fee: 2%
Ownership: 5% - 15%
Term: 4-6 years
Board rights: Observation/BOD seats
Expected return (gross): 17% - 19% 





