Overview
About Us
Parkview Capital Credit, Inc., headquartered in Houston, Texas, is an externally-managed, non-diversified, closed-end investment management company that provides mezzanine debt and equity capital to lower middle market companies throughout the United States. 
Parkview Capital Credit is a closed-end investment fund regulated under the Investment Company Act of 1940, Securities Act of 1933 and Securities Exchange Act of 1934, that provides alternative sources of capital for lower and middle-market companies.
Parkview Capital Credit is managed by Parkview Advisors, LLC, a SEC-registered investment advisor with several years of experience originating and managing debt and equity investments in this space.
Market Opportunity
At Parkview Capital, we bring a wealth of combined investment management, private equity, direct lending experience and strong equity sponsor relationships to the table. We have the ability to efficiently and cost-effectively create a portfolio of lower and middle market credit investments.
Learn more
Our Team
Boasting 25 plus years of combined industry experience, our team has built a solid record of success in the industry.
